Vol / Page:  109
Edition:
Quote:  These parties also brought up from the same spot various other specimens; one parcel of which, consisting of large rich dust and flakes, and exceedingly auriferous quartz (perhaps as rich, gaudy specimens as have yet been seen), was sold by auction by the undersigned yesterday.
Notes:  1852 Dec 21 Gold Circular in 1853 Swainson Auckland 109

